claim.claim-text:
9. In a method for evaluating a patient's risk of sleep apnea, the improvement comprising:
providing an expert computing system;
said expert computing system comparing abnormal respiratory events of a patient with a sleep apnea risk database of sleep apnea risk data, said abnormal respiratory events being based upon monitored physiological information from the patient, said monitored physiological information including pulse oximetry data from the patient;
said expert computing system comparing clinical information of the patient with said sleep apnea risk database, said patient's clinical information being derived from a questionnaire identifying sleep apnea risk factors of the patient; and
said expert computing system generating a report of the patient's risk of sleep apnea.
